OL,3,CMan arrested following sudden death in
OL,4,CEnniskillen
OL,6,FA man has been arrested following a
OL,7,Fsudden death in Co Fermanagh.
OL,9,FPolice said they are investigating the
OL,10,Fincident at Corban Avenue, Enniskillen.
OL,12,F"A man has been arrested in connection
OL,13,Fwith the investigation and is
OL,14,Fcurrently in police custody," they
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,17,F"Officers are at the scene conducting
OL,18,Fa number of enquiries and ask members
OL,19,Fof the public to avoid the area."
